text: Located in coffee shop industrial building in Toh Guan. Price wise is same most western food stall. Taste wise nothing special but doesn't mean not nice. Portion is good enough make you full. Prepared very fast. Paynow or cash. Parking free but limited.

S$2 promo price for the winglet meal. Great value. Good chicken wing, I liked that they didn't use too much marinade. Pasta had real tomato bits. Coleslaw is good. Their other mains tend to be too oily and the sides very sweet. Will be even better if they can use less oil & sugar.
